quran[74]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Ubwo imperuka izaba igeze
  56,2,Ntawe uzashobora guhinyura ukuza kwayo
  56,3,"Izacisha bugufi (abazajya mu muriro), inashyire hejuru (abazajya mu ijuru)"
  56,4,Ubwo isi izatigiswa n’umutingito ukomeye
  56,5,N’imisozi igahindurwa ubuvungukira
  56,6,Maze ikaba umukungugu unyanyagiye
  56,7,(Icyo gihe) muzaba muri mu byiciro bitatu
  56,8,Hari ab’iburyo135; abo bantu b’iburyo ni bantu ki
  56,9,N’ab’ibumoso; abo bantu b’ibumoso ni bantu ki
  56,10,"N’abambere (ni abakurikije amategeko ya Allah bakiri ku isi), abo bazaba ari bo ba mbere (mu kwinjira mu Ijuru)"
  56,11,Abo ni bo bazaba bari hafi (ya Allah)
  56,12,Mu ijuru ryuje ingabire
  56,13,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,14,Na bake mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,15,Bazaba bari ku bitanda bitatswe na zahabu
  56,16,"Babyegamyeho, berekeranye"
  56,17,Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe)
  56,18,"(Bazaba babazengurutsamo) ibikombe, amabirika n’ibirahuri birimo ibinyobwa byiza"
  56,19,Ntibizabatera kurwara umutwe ndetse nta n’ubwo bizabasindisha
  56,20,(Bazaba banazengurutswamo) imbuto bazihitiramo
  56,21,Ndetse n’inyama z’inyoni bazifuza
  56,22,Kandi (hazaba hari) ba Huur ul- a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro n’amaso manini)
  56,23,Bameze nk’inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zikiri mu bubiko bwazo
  56,24,Bizaba ari ibihembo by’ibyo bakoraga
  56,25,Muri ryo (Ijuru) nta magambo adafite akamaro cyangwa se ayatuma bakora ibyaha bazumvamo
  56,26,"Uretse (imvugo yo kuramukanya, igira iti) \"Salamu, Salamu (amahoro, amahoro)"
  56,27,Naho ab’iburyo; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihembo by’abantu b’iburyo)
  56,28,Bazaba (mu Ijuru ririmo) ibiti bya Sidiri bidafite amahwa
  56,29,N’ibitoki by’amaseri agerekeranye
  56,30,No mu gicucu kirambuye (kandi gihoraho)
  56,31,N’amazi ahora atemba
  56,32,Ndetse n’imbuto nyinshi
  56,33,"Ntizizahundura (bitewe n’ihinduka ry’ibihe cyangwa ngo zigire igihe cyo kwera), kandi ntizizaba zibujijwe (kuri bo)"
  56,34,Bazaba banafite ibitanda biri hejuru
  56,35,"Mu by’ukuri, (abagore bo ku isi bazajya mu ijuru) tuzabarema bundi bushya"
  56,36,Maze tubagire amasugi
  56,37,"Bakunda (abagabo babo gusa), kandi ari urungano"
  56,38,(Ibi byose) byateganyirijwe abantu b’iburyo
  56,39,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,40,Na benshi mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,41,Naho abantu b’ibumoso; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihano by’abantu b’ibumoso)
  56,42,Bazaba bari mu muyaga utwika ndetse n’amazi yatuye
  56,43,No mu gicucu cy’umwotsi w’umukara
  56,44,(Icyo gicucu) nta mbeho kizatanga ndetse nta n’icyiza kizagiturukaho
  56,45,"Mu by’ukuri, mbere bari babayeho mu buzima bwo kwinezeza (bigomeka kuri Allah)"
  56,46,Kandi bajyaga batsimbarara ku byaha bihambaye (ntibagire umugambi wo kubyicuza)
  56,47,"Kandi bajyaga bavuga bati \" Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufa (akabora), tuzazurwa koko"
  56,48,N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se
  56,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Yego) rwose, abo hambere n’abo hanyuma"
  56,50,"Bazakoranywa ku munsi uzwi, wagenwe (umunsi w’imperuka)"
  56,51,Nuko mwe abayobye mukanahinyura ukuri
  56,52,Rwose muzarya ku giti cya Zaqumu
  56,53,Maze mucyuzuze inda
  56,54,Mukirenzeho amazi yatuye
  56,55,Muzayanywa nk’ingamiya zinywa zidashira inyota
  56,56,Iryo ni ryo zimano ryabo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  56,57,Ni twe twabaremye. Nonese kuki mutemera (izuka)
  56,58,Ese mutekereza iki ku matembabuzi (amasohora) musohora
  56,59,Ese ni mwe muyarema cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,60,Ni twe twabageneye urupfu kandi ntitwananirwa
  56,61,"Kubasimbuza abameze nka mwe, maze tukabaremamo (amashusho y’) ibindi mutazi"
  56,62,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, mwamenye ukuremwa (kwanyu) kwa mbere. Nonese kuki mutibuka"
  56,63,Ese ntimubona ibyo muhinga
  56,64,"Ese ni mwe mubiha kumera no gukura, cyangwa ni twe tubikora"
  56,65,"Tubishatse twabigira ubushingwe, maze mugakomeza kumirwa"
  56,66,"(Muvuga muti) \"Rwose twaruhiye ubusa"
  56,67,Ahubwo twimwe (ibintu byose)
  56,68,Ese ntimubona amazi munywa
  56,69,Ese ni mwe muyamanura mu bicu cyangwa ni twe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo tuza kubishaka, twari kuyagira urwunyunyu (ntanyobwe). Nonese kuki mudashimira (Allah)"
  56,71,Ese ntimubona umuriro mucana
  56,72,Ese ni mwe mwaremye igiti cyawo (muwukomoramo) cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,73,"Ni twe twawugize urwibutso (rw’umuriro wa Jahanamu), ndetse n’ingirakamaro ku bagenzi (n’abandi bose bawukeneye)"
  56,74,"Ngaho singiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"